  • Constructor Details

    • Person

      public Person(String str, boolean csv)
      Constructor of Person object, either from CSV record, or empty with only ID.
      Parameters:
      str - CSV record if csv is set to true, otherwise ID
      csv - true if the passed string is CSV record

    • Person

      public Person(String id, String name, String type, String dateOfBirth, boolean deceased, String dateOfDeath)
      Constructor of Person object with all data.
      Parameters:
      id - Person's ID
      name - full name
      type - type of entity, either people.person, or people.deceased_person
      dateOfBirth - date of birth
      deceased - boolean whether the person is deceased or not
      dateOfDeath - date of death, which is assigned only if the deceased argument is set to true

    • Person

      public Person(String id, String name, String dateOfBirth, String deceased, String dateOfDeath)
      Constructor of Person object for parsing from Lucene index, which cannot store boolean values, so the deceased argument is passed as string.
      Parameters:
      id - Person's ID
      name - full name
      dateOfBirth - date of birth
      deceased - true if the person is deceased, false if the person is alive
      dateOfDeath - date of death, which is assigned only if the deceased argument is set to true
